            <i class="ri-question-line"></i>
            <h4>How are prices updated?</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-7">
            <p>
              Most prices are automatically updated at least once a day. For a lot of retailers, prices are updated 
              more often than that. However, this site does not guarantee that prices are correct. 
            </p>
          </div>
